# Generated market-report intermediates
# Keep the public showcase PDF and compact build-metadata.json eligible for
# selective publication; raw responses, normalized datasets, charts and the
# rendered HTML remain reproducible local build products.
reports/market/**/raw/
reports/market/**/data/
reports/market/**/charts/
reports/market/**/report.html
